<Paragraph FontWeight="Bold" FontFamily="Cambria" FontSize="16">
Features
</Paragraph>

<List Margin="25,0,0,0">
<ListItem><Paragraph>Essential Chart for WPF supports customization of large and small value changes in the horizontal and vertical scroll bars.</Paragraph></ListItem>
<ListItem><Paragraph>The built-in Zoom tool can be invoked for zooming options.</Paragraph></ListItem>
<ListItem><Paragraph>It supports zooming via commands such as <Bold>ZoomIn</Bold> and <Bold>ZoomOut</Bold>.</Paragraph></ListItem>
<ListItem><Paragraph>Zooming can also be performed programmatically.</Paragraph></ListItem>
<ListItem><Paragraph>It supports Panning command to pan the Zoomed area</Paragraph></ListItem>
</List>


<Paragraph FontWeight="Bold" FontFamily="Cambria" FontSize="16">
Interactive Features</Paragraph>


<List Margin="25,0,0,0">

<ListItem>
<Paragraph>The <Bold>"Show ZoomButton"</Bold> check box enables or disables the chart zooming tool kit. </Paragraph>
</ListItem>

<ListItem>
<Paragraph>The <Bold>"Zoom-In"</Bold> combo box will help in selecting the key gestures for a zoom-in.</Paragraph>
</ListItem>

<ListItem>
<Paragraph>The <Bold>"Zoom-Out"</Bold> combo box will help in selecting the key gestures for a zoom-out.</Paragraph>
</ListItem>

<ListItem>
<Paragraph>The <Bold>"Panning"</Bold> combo box will help in selecting the key gestures for a zoom-pan.</Paragraph>
</ListItem>


<ListItem>
<Paragraph>The <Bold>"Zoom Factor X"</Bold> combo box will let you select the zoom factor for the primary axis.</Paragraph>
</ListItem>

<ListItem>
<Paragraph>The <Bold>"Zoom Factor Y"</Bold> combo box allows you to select the zoom factor for the secondary axis.</Paragraph>
</ListItem>


<ListItem>
<Paragraph>The <Bold>"Zoom X Range"</Bold> text box displays the Zoomed X range.</Paragraph>
</ListItem>

<ListItem>
<Paragraph>The <Bold>"Zoom Y Range"</Bold> text box Displays the Zoomed Y range.</Paragraph>
</ListItem>

<ListItem>
<Paragraph>The <Bold>HorizontalBar LargeChange</Bold> combo box lets you select the horizontal scroll bar large change.</Paragraph>
</ListItem>

<ListItem>
<Paragraph>The <Bold>VerticalBar LargeChange</Bold> combo box lets you select the vertical scroll bar large change.</Paragraph>
</ListItem>

<ListItem>
<Paragraph>The <Bold>HorizontalBar SmallChange</Bold> combo box lets you select the horizontal scroll bar small change.</Paragraph>
</ListItem>

<ListItem>
<Paragraph>The <Bold>VerticalBar SmallChange</Bold> combo box lets you select the vertical scroll bar small change.</Paragraph>
</ListItem>



</List>
